name: MIMECAST [URL Blocked - <%= category %>]
description: This rule looks for emails with malicious URLs that Mimecast blocked.

name: MIMECAST [Email Rejected - <%= exceptiontype %>]
description: The rule detects emails with malicious attachments that have been rejected by Mimecast.

name: MIMECAST [Malicious File]
description: The rule detects emails with malicious attachments that have been detected, by Mimecast.
query: class:mimecast has:virus NOT has:action NOT srcipv4:$exclusions.global.srcipv4
